{"url": "https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/james-corden-children-gay-relationships/", "text": "The TV host has always been an ally. | Photo: YouTube/The Late Late Show with James Corden\n\nLate night host James Corden has the best answer if his children ever ask him about gay relationships.\n\nThey haven\u2019t yet because gay people have always been a part of their lives.\n\nCorden opened up about their family life and raising his children to be accepting in an Attitude interview.\n\n\u2018They haven\u2019t brought it up, but we have lots of gay friends \u2013 like our friends Chris and Mark \u2013 who have come over a lot and stayed with us,\u2019 he said. \u2018I think my son has never questioned it as it\u2019s always been there.\u2019\n\nCorden, who\u2019s currently the host of The Late Late Show, has three children with his wife Julia Carey.\n\nIf any of his children ever ask, though, he has the perfect answer.\n\n\u2018I would know what those answers were, which is that these are simply two men that really love each other in the same way I love Mummy and Grandma loves Grandad and that\u2019s it.\u2019\n\nThat\u2019s a perfect answer.\n\nBorn that way\n\nCorden added \u2018no one is born wanting to dislike anyone\u2019 and his parents raised him to be accepting. Now it\u2019s a lesson he\u2019s passing on to his own children.\n\nHis support of the community is nothing new.\n\nSoon after Trump wanted to ban trans soldiers from the movie, Corden did a number supporting trans troops.\n\nThe interview describes him as an LGBT ally and he said he has an affinity with the community. However, he\u2019s aware of his own privilege too.\n\n\u2018I\u2019ve always looked different, not the societal ideal, but I\u2019ve never felt like an outsider to the extent that my gay friends have felt. It would be naive of me to think I have.\u2019", "images": ["https://www.gaystarnews.com/wp-content/plugins/special-recent-posts/cache/srpthumb-p281606-50x50-no.jpg", "https://www.ga